    "causal_summary": "Five-iteration SOL xhigh-fast deep-research lineage on a no-wrong-door routing protocol where any mode can accept intake and offer a typed transfer through a bounded INTAKE→OFFERED→ACCEPTED→ACTIVE state machine, where acceptance transfers execution ownership but is distinct from completion, authority stays destination-local via a short-lived scoped lease, and cost is bounded by an idempotent transfer id, visited-mode set, hop budget, deadline, and at most one clarification turn — used only on the ambiguous path, never replacing confident one-shot routes.",
